name: Golf #01 - California - "Red Valley"
description:
A 1 of 50 collection based on the adventures and videos of World Twilight Golfer. Each piece is from a golf course in each State of the USA. Only 10 art pieces can be produced as of 2021. All sales will go towards traveling and making YouTube videos of future golf courses. Anyone holding Golf #1-#10 will be airdropped Golf #11-#20.

Here is the video for Red Valley: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Pa7n0aN5IKI

Please subscribe to World Twilight Golfer on YouTube!!
